eplyTime":"2020-02-26T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"ff系列 - 想大鬧六合彩直播<br />\n<br />\n有冇J2想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap334&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6XzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=6b299e35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap334</a><br />\n10.妨礙獎券抽獎的進行<br />\n任何人妨礙或阻礙任何獎券抽獎的進行，或在正進行或行將進行獎券抽獎的場地或其附近製造任何騷擾，即屬犯罪，循簡易程序定罪後，可處罰款$1,000及監禁3個月。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"3351be32fb6491b7bf55fcb662d96de83e7c829e","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe5b0b72015b479c17a471e941f3df6d7a2b5f1","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed90d209d9a474853a1105818ee0301e5726dd3d","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"為在不影響公眾衛生的情況下滿足馬迷的需要，馬會決定由2020年3月2日起，即下周一，每星期兩天開放部份場外投注站，並強調在有關安排下，場外投注站僅會提供上述有限度的服務；<span style=\"color: red;\">場內不會提供賽馬及足球投注服務，六合彩獎券也會繼續暫停。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb669d5f6486b86c1482ed832c3577fd4393e195","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:44:38.000Z","msg":"同拍檔常公子吹水，他說現時投注站不開，連六合彩都無得賣，小市民好鼓譟。我回家後，上網看高登財經，有人留言說：「Auntie，馬又照跑，波又照賭，六合彩就唔開，乜嘢玩法？」（按：Auntie是高登術語。）<br />\n<br />\n其實我都不明點解不開六合彩，電話投注，按掣買咪得囉，網上投注又得，啲人用慣咗，可能以後用電話買，仲慳番啲人手𠻹呀！要知道，六合彩是維穩工具，點可以停㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d249926307091eb6b6c6c6d25838b45cc60160ea","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f844d4ad9d3a1b2e9758dc05178d6abf5ecb963d","tid":1898993,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"六合彩又唔搞，直接瓜分la diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328579c693802edb3844abdcb3296d74240d47b3","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d249926307091eb6b6c6c6d25838b45cc60160ea","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f844d4ad9d3a1b2e9758dc05178d6abf5ecb963d","tid":1898993,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"六合彩又唔搞，直接瓜分la diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fad34608a276df6b16155233f3c64c78f36fc7c","tid":1898993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}